      "author": "s1m4ne",
      "description": "## What's Changed\n\n### New Features\n* Add session layout version history with Time Machine-style compaction (#28)\n  - Layouts are automatically saved to history before any overwrite\n  - Tiered compaction: all within 1h, hourly for 1-24h, daily for 1-7d, weekly for 7-30d\n  - Periodic snapshot timer detects structural layout changes\n  - History viewer modal with date-grouped entries\n  - Mod+RMB quick restore on status bar (Cmd on Mac, Ctrl on Windows/Linux)\n  - Settings in Sessions tab (snapshot interval, quick restore, confirm before restore)\n  - Enabled by default\n\n### Improvements\n* Add tabbed settings UI with 4 tabs (General, Sessions, Groups, Advanced)\n* Add plugin icon (panels-top-left) for installed plugins list (#32)\n* Add reload button, status bar context menu, and refactor session menus (#30)\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/s1m4ne/obsidian-workspace-plus/compare/0.6.4...0.7.0",
